### Data Sources, Legal & Usage Notice

 All resulting data is sourced from, including but not limited to, OMDB (CC BY-NC 4.0), under their respective terms. Please review and comply with the terms of all data providers.

This project uses data from the following sources:

> **Movie data provided by** OMDB API (https://www.omdbapi.com/)
> 
> Licensed under CC BY-NC 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/)

> **IMDb data is used solely for initial filtering (IDs and ratings) to select which movies to process.**
> No content, metadata, or descriptive information is used from IMDb; all resulting data and outputs are sourced from OMDB and are not derivative works of IMDb data.
